---
---

<section class="how-it-works" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label">How it works</span>
    <h2>Three commands.<br />That's it.</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">From zero to production in under 5 minutes. ShipNode handles building, syncing, process management, reverse proxying, and HTTPS.</p>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Initialize</h3>
          <p>Auto-detects your framework, suggests defaults, creates config.</p>
          <div class="step-code"><code>$ shipnode init</code></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Setup server</h3>
          <p>Installs Node.js, PM2, and Caddy on your server. Run once.</p>
          <div class="step-code"><code>$ shipnode setup</code></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Deploy</h3>
          <p>Zero-downtime deploy with health checks and auto-rollback.</p>
          <div class="step-code"><code>$ shipnode deploy</code></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="diagram">
      <div class="diagram-card">
        <pre><code><span class="d-muted">Your Laptop</span>                    <span class="d-muted">Your Server</span>
<span class="d-muted">──────────────</span>                  <span class="d-muted">────────────</span>
shipnode deploy  <span class="d-accent">───rsync──▶</span>   /var/www/myapp/
                                 ├── <span class="d-green">current/</span>       <span class="d-muted">← active release</span>
                                 ├── releases/      <span class="d-muted">← timestamped</span>
                                 ├── shared/.env    <span class="d-muted">← persistent</span>
                                 └── <span class="d-blue">PM2 + Caddy</span>    <span class="d-muted">← process + HTTPS</span></code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-it-works {
    padding: var(--space-4xl) var(--space-xl);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  .section-desc {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    max-width: 540px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }
  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }
  .step {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    transition: border-color var(--transition-base), box-shadow var(--transition-base);
  }
  .step:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-glow);
  }
  .step-number {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: var(--accent-glow);
    color: var(--accent-hover);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  .step h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }
  .step p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  .step-code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--accent-hover);
    background: var(--bg-code);
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
  }
  .diagram-card {
    background: var(--bg-code);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    overflow-x: auto;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  .diagram-card pre {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .d-muted { color: var(--text-tertiary); }
  .d-accent { color: var(--accent-hover); }
  .d-green { color: var(--green); }
  .d-blue { color: #60a5fa; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
